{"tid":2175292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想你嬲想制造無力感，大家要學識保持初心","createTime":"2020-08-26T11:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T06:54:05.000Z","uid":19817,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de82d651af19160e513eb59ef091786cc411187c","tid":2175292,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"由佢高調話會作出更大既拘捕<br />\n已經知道會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地要做既係不斷拉攏藍營令佢地唔會轉黃<br />\n<br />\n無力係事實<br />\n要接受無論抗唔抗爭都只會有愈來愈大既打壓<br />\n但心態先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n加速主義既第一日就預左黎緊會係咁, 預料之內<br />\n接受到既留低 接受唔到既去海外<br />\n<br />\n仲有放負抽水話輸左果d，根本唔明咩係攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會抽水白羅斯泰國台灣？<br />\n除左係五毛pr仲會係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cf01436fc7d9a9ae7e3aa3e79ba9d0ff4ca9f5","tid":2175292,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62251694993a93e541b0824213ceaa54a932fc5f","tid":2175292,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9e18dd9f2b8b661d5eeebd00fc721b70a10d4a","tid":2175292,"uid":42819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af6f7cc99a08067da7d7170ee354c7d1468f2fe","tid":2175292,"uid":342250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20